Package: Grmd
Version: 0.1.3
Date: 2018-01-20
Title: A package for improving publishing through word-processor integration
Author: Max Gordon <max@gforge.se>
Maintainer: Max Gordon <max@gforge.se>
Description: The new rmarkdown-package developed by and included in RStudio
    allows for simplifications of the porting to word documents.
    Apart from having a direct port it allows tailoring of formatters
    that make the conversion between html and MS Word virtually seemless.
License: GPL (>= 3) | file LICENSE
URL: http://gforge.se
BugReports: https://github.com/gforge/Grmd/issues
Biarch: yes
Imports:
    rmarkdown,
    XML,
    knitr
Suggests:
    testthat
Roxygen: list(wrap = TRUE)
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
